### Commit Process

1. (Optionally) Fork the `develop` branch.
2. If the {{path('.github/demo.gif', link='md')}} will change, run
   `bash ./scripts/generate-animation.sh`, this will generate a new
   {{path('.github/demo.gif', link='md')}}.
